The Coming of... Sub-Mariner! Chapter 1 "On the Trail of the Torch!"
results.description: Flashback to previous issue. The Fantastic Four is searching for the runaway Human Torch.

results.title: Chapter 2 Enter the Sub-Mariner
results.description: The runaway Human Torch finds the amnesiac Sub-Mariner. Revival of the Sub-Mariner as a noble anti-hero.

results.title: Chapter 3 Let the World Beware!
results.description: Human Torch drops the Sub-Mariner into the sea and Namor the Sub-Mariner regains his memory.

results.title: Chapter 4 Sub-Mariner's Revenge!
results.description: The Sub-Mariner sends Giganto to smash New York.

results.title: Chapter 5 "Return to the Deep!"
results.description: The Thing walks into Giganto with a bomb and blows him up. The Human Torch sweeps the Sub-Mariner and Giganto away into the sea. The Sub-Mariner says "I'll be back!"
